{"tid":1825924,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"需要外國巴打做說客, 試下遊說基金經理降低對中国和香港投資金額","createTime":"2020-01-15T17:03:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-17T10:03:16.000Z","uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"18df64c9d4324afcb4d15fc42f01f5b03c97cbba","tid":1825924,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T17:03:31.000Z","msg":"之前諗過告上國際法律, 當然呢個應該都要做<br />\n但要告上法律, 成功後當地政府再立例, 禁止買中資, 這樣太遲了, 時間以年計<br />\n仲要中途, 有強国出橫手, 隨時失敗, 太多未知數<br />\n<br />\n需要外國巴打做說客, 試下遊說基金經理降低對中国和香港投資<br />\n其實外國有很多大大小小的基金公司, 而且唔一定個個和強国有什麼關係, 收受強国好處<br />\n基金有一定彈性, 在可動用範圍內改變投資策略和目標<br />\n很多基金經理打份工, 另加花紅, 根據特定的指引限制下去投資各種型債券, 股票, 基金, 外匯等<br />\n<br />\n可以試下動之以情<br />\n如<br />\n&quot;香港的年青人只是為左香港的自由和民主而上街, 甚至願意付上自己將來和性命, 但依然受到殘暴和殘忍的獨裁政權狠狠地鎮壓. 很多年青人因此為左失去了性命&quot;<br />\n<br />\n希望基金經理降低對中国和香港投資金額, 我相信應該有限制要投定至少比例金額到中国和香港度, 但至少將對中国和香港投資金額比例降到最低"},{"pid":"85954ea9cf1e89f83e4ebc41af32b6768148e16e","tid":1825924,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T17:05:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">寧願徒勞無功, 也不坐以待斃</span>"},{"pid":"651bc33d7cc348218bb881a45534cec3b216aee2","tid":1825924,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T17:10:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"728cc7eee914fdb4b2b0e2fb6c5c3997468e3d9d","tid":1825924,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T17:11:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09f6fda3759249022b356b1738edf73f764c91e3","tid":1825924,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T17:11:55.000Z","msg":"Too much"},{"pid":"2b489235131473e293fcc5a7676decb8696b6c09","tid":1825924,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T17:12:39.000Z","msg":"容易D會係做股東維權"},{"pid":"ef7b37e10ae29e46634f7860b11965eccf039d1d","tid":1825924,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b489235131473e293fcc5a7676decb8696b6c09","tid":1825924,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T17:12:39.000Z","msg":"容易D會係做股東維權"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T17:14:37.000Z","msg":"即係點?"},{"pid":"9844a9c23d25cb32088051fd1269794cdd8e0867","tid":1825924,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T09:39:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有冇人聯絡到"},{"pid":"213892be58b21b013c1d9a4f624cedc86fbb5a07","tid":1825924,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T10:03:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}